_sText:
Small combat map with dynamic gameplay. Made by me special for Russian Front Clan

----------------
**Installation:**

Extract the .bsp and .nav files into this folder:
...\Steam\SteamApps\common\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps

----------------
**Features:**

- 36 spawnpoints;
- Small sized
- Balanced
- Buy zones;
- Optimized
- HDR support
- .nav file
